snippet.title: Class Overhaul Trailer - Warhammer 40,000: Darktide
snippet.description:
The Xbox release will include Darktide’s biggest update yet, overhauling the class & feat systems while introducing talent trees. These changes will allow you to create more unique builds and playstyles.

Patch #13 will release alongside Darktide's Xbox release on October 4.

Learn more about Darktide:
